Prof. '''Branwen Kiemute Okpako''' (yavutse 25 Gashyantare 1969), yavukiye muri [[nijeriya]] gusa akorera umwuga wo gutunganya amaflimi mu [[budage]]  .  Azwi cyane nkumuyobozi wa firime zizwi cyane''The Education of Auma Obama'', ''Dirt for Dinner'' and ''Landing''. . Usibye gutanga  icyerekezo, ni n'umwanditsi, producer, sinema, umwanditsi wa firime ndetse numwarimu. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 25 Gashyantare 1969 i Lagos, muri [[Nijeriya]].  Afite imyaka 16, yimukiye i Wales .  Mu 1991, Okpako yabonye impamyabumenyi ya B.Sc. mu bumenyi bwa politiki yakuye muri kaminuza ya Bristol, mu [[Bwongereza]] nyuma akaza gukurikira amasomo ya MFA ahwanye na filime iyobowe na Academy ya Filime na Televiziyo yo mu Budage Berlin GmbH, Berlin (DFFB) mu 1999. 

Yashakanye na Johannes Brandrup, nyuma baza gutandukana.

== Umwuga ==
Mugihe mu mwaka wa nyuma wa DFFB, yakoze firime ye ya mbere ya ''Dreckfresser'' mu 2000.  Filime yibanze ku bapolisi ba mbere b'abirabura mu Budage bw'Iburasirazuba. Filime yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi mpuzamahanga harimo Intambwe Zibanza: Igihembo cy’Abadage Newcomer Igihembo cya Film Documentary 2000, IG Media Award i Dok Leipzig mu 2000, Igihembo cyatanzwe kuva kugurisha 2000. Yatsindiye kandi igihembo cyiza cya Filime nziza mu cyumweru cya 24 cya Duisburg. Mu 2001, iyi filime yahawe igihembo cya Leta ya Bavariya Igihembo cyiswe “Intare ikiri nto” ndetse na filime nziza yo gutanga impamyabumenyi mu iserukiramuco rya Docs Dubrovnik.  

Usibye sinema, Okpako ni Umwarimu wungirije mu ishami rya Sinema n’itangazamakuru rya Digital muri kaminuza ya California, Davis .  

